Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and got pregnant\Nagainst your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you decided\Nthat you would kill Hirasaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!\NThe doctor never raped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a lie! The father of my\Nbaby is the man I love, Ryuji Hirasaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoya Ohkawa sent this\Nthrough his manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know nothing{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says there's nothing\Nleft for him to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the reason behind the\Nsuicide of Narumi Jinguji is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, I checked with old classmates\Nof Narumi Jinguji and Ryuji Hirasaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but all their mutual friends have\Nbecome successful and knew nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Living together with{\i0}\N{\i1}a girl you trained{\i0}... {\i1}Isn't that cute{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That impudence{\i0}\N{\i1}hasn't changed at all since back then{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an acceptance party going on.\NDo you want to come, Hirasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can all introduce ourselves, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To become a doctor,\Nwe can't be just about studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We finally finished our entry exams,\Nso let's unwind a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Q-Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... I think I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. Well, maybe next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was our first meeting{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.85,0:23:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was a strange guy{\i0}.\N{\i1}That's all I thought{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, for some reason,{\i0}\N{\i1}he was never far from my mind{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hirasaka wasn't like the{\i0}\N{\i1}other idiots who came to school{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to become a village doctor,{\i0}\N{\i1}or to carry on the family practice{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.93,0:23:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I was slowly beginning to{\i0}\N{\i1}find him more and more interesting{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. Now, everyone watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This, and then this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This person truly wanted{\i0}\N{\i1}to learn medicine, I thought{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why did you decide\Nto become a doctor, Hirasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially in gynecology...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.33,0:23:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just asking. Ah!\NIt must be because you like women!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love women.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.14,0:24:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I respect them a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.87,0:24:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because all people were born\Nfrom women.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The history of the human race\Nwas built by women.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.38,0:24:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am in utter awe of a woman's\Nmysterious ability to create.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to hold these women\Nin high regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.56,0:24:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided\Nto pick gynecology.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.49,0:24:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. I'm sorry,\NI didn't mean to tease you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.13,0:24:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think that you had thought\Nso much about it, Hirasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.64,0:24:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think she's a jumper!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.94,0:24:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.51,0:24:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirasaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.18,0:24:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you hear me? Someone!\NDid someone call an ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.15,0:24:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.85,0:24:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't do anything{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.39,0:25:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot... To throw away your own life\Nafter you were born through...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.03,0:25:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,such a miraculous joining of\Na male seed and female egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.27,0:25:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how he looked, I thought{\i0}\N{\i1}that this was the kind of person{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.37,0:25:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who really should be a doctor,{\i0}\N{\i1}and I honestly respected him{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.31,0:25:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even after that, Hirasaka never{\i0}\N{\i1}showed up at any student parties,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.48,0:25:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and all he did was study{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.72,0:25:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even when I was training,{\i0}\N{\i1}I was with Hirasaka{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.09,0:25:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know if this was a{\i0}\N{\i1}coincidence or if it was fate{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.53,0:25:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.91,0:25:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm completely wiped out.\NHow about you, Hirasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.54,0:25:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel very complete.\NIt's best to be molded by experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.78,0:25:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's your research? Is it progressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.39,0:26:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm focusing on characteristic\Ninfection symptoms, which is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.79,0:26:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, pretty soon, I'm planning an\Nunrelated ultimate experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.03,0:26:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ultimate experiment? Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.73,0:26:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd love it if you would help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.70,0:26:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. Ask me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.84,0:26:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I'd appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.22,0:26:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That night would be a turning point{\i0}\N{\i1}for the rest of my life{\i0}...
